# Contents

This directory contains C. opilio transcriptomes and Uniprot database. They can be downloaded at the following links: 

C. opilio_Molting gland transcriptome: https://gannet.fish.washington.edu/seashell/snaps/HBXI01.fasta
C. opilio Eyestalk ganglia transcriptome: https://gannet.fish.washington.edu/seashell/snaps/HBWO01.fasta
UniProt Swiss-Prot database: https://ftp.uniprot.org/pub/databases/uniprot/current_release/knowledgebase/complete/uniprot_sprot.fasta.gz
